code: @Override protected void doStart() throws Exception {     super.doStart().     ((AvroComponent) getEndpoint().getComponent()).register(getEndpoint().getConfiguration().getUriAuthority(), getEndpoint().getConfiguration().getMessageName(), this). }

@Override protected void doStop() throws Exception {     ((AvroComponent) getEndpoint().getComponent()).unregister(getEndpoint().getConfiguration().getUriAuthority(), getEndpoint().getConfiguration().getMessageName()).     super.doStop(). }
